com.microsoft.band

Interface BandClient


  • public interface BandClient
    Client for communicating with a Microsoft Band through Microsoft Health's band communication service

    • Method Detail

      • connect

        BandPendingResult<ConnectionState> connect()

        Method to bind to Microsoft Health's band communication service and attempt a connection to the Microsoft Band

        Warning: BandPendingResult.await() of the returned BandPendingResult may not be called from a UI thread as doing so would create an infinite block

        Returns:
        A BandPendingResult with a ConnectionState return value representing the current connection state of this client to the Microsoft Health band communication service and the Microsoft Band that could potentially throw a BandException with the following error type: BandErrorType.SERVICE_ERROR
        Throws:
        java.lang.SecurityException - if the following permission is not declared in your manifest: com.microsoft.band.service.access.BIND_BAND_SERVICE

      • disconnect

        BandPendingResult<java.lang.Void> disconnect()
        Method to unbind from Microsoft Health's band communication service
        Returns:
        A BandPendingResult with a Void return value that could potentially throw a BandException with the following error type: BandErrorType.TIMEOUT_ERROR

      • getFirmwareVersion

        BandPendingResult<java.lang.String> getFirmwareVersion()
                                                       throws BandIOException
        Method to get the firmware version of the Microsoft Band
        Returns:
        A BandPendingResult with a String return value containing the Microsoft Band's firmware version that could potentially throw a BandException with the following error types: BandErrorType.DEVICE_ERROR and BandErrorType.TIMEOUT_ERROR
        Throws:
        BandIOException - if Microsoft Health's band communication service is not available

        Throws:
        BandIOException - if Microsoft Health's band communication service is not available
